condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.A.1(a) | Description :Recipient shall ensure that MOI, through the PMU, implements and monitorsthe project. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.A.1(b) | Description :Recipient shall ensure that MOI (i) maintains the PMU with suitable staff;and (ii) its Directorate of Roads, Bridges, and Flood Control. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.A.2 | Description :The Recipient shall maintain its National Development Agency, throughout theperiod of implementation of the Project, to oversee and monitor all aspects of the Project implementation | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.B | Description :The Recipient shall ensure that the MOI adopts, not later than the EffectiveDate, the Project Operational Manual, satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :26-Aug-2011
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.C | Description :The Recipient shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordance withthe provisions of the Anti-Corruption Guidelines. | Frequency :Monthly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.D.1 | Description :The Recipient shall carry out the Project in accordance with the EnvironmentalManagement Plan and the Resettlement Policy Framework, and any Resettlement Action Plans. | Frequency :Quarterly
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2 - I.D.6 | Description :Recipient shall regularly collect, compile, information on the status ofcompliance with safeguard documents | Frequency :Quarterly
